&lt;h1 id="having-kids"&gt;Having Kids&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;December 2019&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Before I had kids, I was afraid of having kids. Up to that point I felt about kids the way the young Augustine felt about living virtuously. I&amp;rsquo;d have been sad to think I&amp;rsquo;d never have children. But did I want them now? No.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>